4'></a></td><td><a href='/photo.php?source=all&color=all&list=search&foreigntype=S&foreigntype_id=460'><img src="/images/imagemagick/tmb_ship_petrofbay3.jpg" border='0' alt=''The Royal Court of Neptunus Rex': line crossing ceremony aboard USS Petrof Bay, Aug 1944'></a></td></tr></table><a href='/photo.php?source=all&color=all&list=search&foreigntype=S&foreigntype_id=460'>See all 9 photographs of Escort Carrier USS Petrof Bay</a><br /><br /><br /><br />
